new text Frontend development deals with the user interface and user experience, using technologies like HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to create responsive and interactive designs. Backend development focuses on server-side logic, database interactions, and application functionality, using languages like Python, Java, and PHP to handle data processing, server configuration, and user authentication. Frontend is what users see and interact with directly, while backend ensures the application runs smoothly behind the scenes.

/*@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap');*/


/**,body{font-family: "Noto Sans", sans-serif;}*/
body{overflow-x: hidden;overflow-y: scroll;width: 100vw;height:100%}

#rightSideBarPinBtn.pin-rotated{transform: rotate(45deg);}
#rightSideBarPinBtn{transform: rotate(0);}

.each-topic,
.sidebar-subjectBtn,
.chapter-title
{position:relative;padding-left:2rem!important}


#prompt-offcanvas-hide-btn{background:var(--prompt-btn-bg);backdrop-filter:blur(3px);transform:translate(-50%,-100%);}

.each-topic::before,
.sidebar-subjectBtn::before,
.chapter-title::before
{position:absolute;font-family: "Font Awesome 6 Pro";transform:translate(-170%);font-weight:700}

.each-topic::before{content:'\f02e';}
.sidebar-subjectBtn::before{content:'\f5d9';}
.chapter-title::before{content:'\f04b';}

.selectedEl{outline:2px solid var(--bs-primary)!important;background:var(--box-hover-bg);border-radius:.2rem}
#element-content-container{height:auto;background: var(--element-container-bg);}
#element-content-container.selectedEl,.modal-body.selectedEl{outline:none!important;background:inherit}
.each-content-section{min-height:200px!important;max-height:auto;}
#element-content-container[data-has-new-content = 'true'] .each-content-section{border:1px solid var(--border-color)!important}
.active-list-icon{border:2px solid var(--bs-primary)}

.hl{padding:.1em .4em;border-radius:.2em;font-size:.9em;margin:0 .2rem;box-shadow:none}
.hl-default{color: var(--body-font-color);background: var(--hover-bg);}


.target{outline:2px solid var(--body-font-color)!important}

#headerMsgContainer{opacity:1}
#headerMsgContainer.fade{
  animation: msgBoxFade 2s;
}

@keyframes msgBoxFade{
	0%{opacity:0}
	100%{opacity:1}
}



#leftsideBar-subject-list .sidebar-subjectBtn.active{color:var(--link-color);}

#nav-reload-bar{position:relative}
#nav-reload-bar.load::before{position:absolute;content:'';width:5%;bottom:0;start:0;background: crimson;height:2px;border-radius: 1em;animation:reloadBar 4s ease;}

@keyframes reloadBar{
	25%{width:10%;translate: translateX(10%);opacity:1}
	75%{width:30%;translate: translateX(40%)}	
	100%{width:100%;translate: translateX(70%);opacity:.7}		
}
